  "prompt": "What is a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Power County ID?",
  "response": "While I can't provide real-time recommendations, some reputable inpatient drug and alcohol rehab centers located near Power County, Idaho can be found through various search methods such as online directories, review websites, and local resource centers. Here are a few steps you can take to identify a good rehab center:\n\n1. **Online Research:** Use websites like SAMHSA\u2019s treatment locator (https://findtreatment.samhsa.gov/) or other addiction treatment directories to find centers close to Power County.\n\n2. **Reviews and Testimonials:** Websites like Yelp, Google Maps, and Healthgrades can offer reviews and ratings from individuals who have used these services.\n\n3. **Contact Local Health Services:** Power County health services or community health centers can often refer you to reputable inpatient rehab centers in the region.\n\n4. **Check Accreditation:** Confirm that the rehab center is accredited by organizations such as the Commission on Accreditation of Rehabilitation Facilities (CARF) or Joint Commission.\n\n5. **Consult Professionals:** Speak with medical providers, therapists, or social workers who might have insider knowledge regarding high-quality rehab facilities.\n\nMake sure to consider factors like the specific treatment programs offered, staff credentials, therapy types, success rates, and aftercare support when choosing a facility.",
